This paper discusses the connections between dynamic programming and (constrained) convex optimization in the context of reinforcement learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
